ure of shock trajectories in magnetic fields through which the\norigin of the explosion and the centre defined by extrapolated proper motions\nof BN, I and n may be brought into spatial coincidence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Mar 2012 11:44:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-03-15"}
